  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISES] [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, when we came to Siemiatycze, sort-- the situation there-- people were going and coming, and, well, my parents were so very happy that we got out of Germany and that, hopefully, that will be so, for us, the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there was a lot of confusion because a lot of people were going back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We met quite a few people-- well, my father's friends-- like that would come and say that, oh, they'd left some family in Warsaw or somewhere else, and the situation in-- in the Russia occupied zone is not so hot, and they're going back.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, and we-- so anyway, we were confused because we thought that this is where we are going to stay, and very hopefully, and here, we saw people, young people, going back.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Unfortunately, later on, history proved them very wrong because thousands of Jews would survive if they would not [INAUDIBLE] they wouldn't go back, if they would stay on, and so-- but-- but for us, it was a bit of confusion.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, so we stayed in Siemiatycze for almost a week, or perhaps a bit more, and then my father decided-- or probably he had it in plan already before-- that we are going to Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Lutsk was a very big city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In a-- and my father hoped to be able to get maybe some kind-- he had some friends there that he knew from before.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He thought that perhaps he'll be able to get a job, and we came to Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That family that we came to was a very lovely family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were very nice people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were quite wealthy people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They helped us to establish.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
